Definition: something or someone that has suffered ruin or dilapidation
Example: the house was a wreck when they bought it; thanks to that quack I am a human wreck
Synonyms: verb, contact, decline, something, or, someone, that, has, suffered, ruin, dilapidation, the, house, was, a, when, they, bought, it, thanks, to, quack, I, am, human
Category: noun.state
